        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Hey there, fellow creator! If you're looking to up your video game without the hassle, CapCut is your new best friend. This AI-powered editor from ByteDance has blown up for making pro-level editing a breeze, whether you're on mobile or desktop. I've been using it for months, and it's transformed how I produce content—saving time and boosting creativity. Ready to dive in? Let's get started with a simple step-by-step tutorial.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
