        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Advanced Editing Tips",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you're comfortable, dive into color correction and audio enhancements. Use the \"Adjust\" panel to tweak brightness, contrast, and saturation for that cinematic look. The audio tools let you add music, voiceovers, and sound effects seamlessly. I often use the AI clipper to trim long videos into highlights automatically—great for repurposing content.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
