      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Exporting and Sharing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://capcutaffiliateprogram.pxf.io/c/6249333/1876054/2247"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you're done, hit \"Export\" and choose your resolution—up to 4K for crisp quality. CapCut lets you share directly to platforms like YouTube, TikTok, or Instagram. The free version includes a small watermark, but it's barely noticeable. For watermark-free exports and more features, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "try CapCut Pro",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "—it's worth it for serious creators.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
