          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CapCut constantly rolls out updates that keep it ahead of the curve. Recent additions include enhanced AI scripts for auto-generating video outlines and improved template customization. I tested the new voice changer tool last week, and it added a fun twist to my tutorials. Stay updated by checking out ",
