        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tool is perfect for beginners, social media influencers, marketers, and educators. Whether you're making quick reels, detailed tutorials, or promotional content, CapCut adapts to your needs. Its affordability and ease of use make it a standout—I've recommended it to friends who went from zero to confident editors in days. For more on why it's a top choice, see ",
